2. Go module dependencies (go.mod)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This project depends on a number of Go modules listed in go.mod, each
governed by its own license. None of the runtime dependencies are GPL or
AGPL; all are permissive (MIT, BSD-2/3-Clause, Apache-2.0, or MPL-2.0).
A full list with license text per module can be regenerated with:

    go install github.com/google/go-licenses@latest
    go-licenses report ./...

